headline: Halliburton Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: HOUSTON, September 18, 2025--Halliburton Company (NYSE: HAL) will host a conference call on Tuesday, October 21, 2025, to discuss its third quarter 2025 financial results. The call will begin at 8:00 a.m. CT (9:00 a.m. ET).
